{
  "text": "To sum as an educational tool, technology finds a number of applications in and outside the classroom. Many researchers [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] observed that the development of online technologies has brought new ways of learning and teaching.",
